      <title>特朗普告诉内阁，他希望美联储能降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-tells-cabinet-he-hopes-fed-will-lower-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统重申了他要求美联储在周一的内阁会议上降低利率的呼吁，因为他继续推动中央银行采取货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-tells-cabinet-he-hopes-fed-will-lower-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 16:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安（Erdogan）在投资者不安中发誓要承诺经济政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/erdogan-vows-commitment-to-economic-policy-amid-investor-unease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）承诺对他在2023年接受的对投资者友好的经济政策的承诺，这指责反对他最大的竞争对手所激发的市场波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/erdogan-vows-commitment-to-economic-policy-amid-investor-unease</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 16:08:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普为什么想要乌克兰的矿物质以及提供什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-minerals-and-rare-earths-deal-what-does-trump-want</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在3月中旬表示，赢得乌克兰自然资源一部分的交易将“很快”签署，因为他继续努力结束俄罗斯在该国的三年战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-minerals-and-rare-earths-deal-what-does-trump-want</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 15:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CBS的60分钟敦促发布成绩单以进行未来的政治访谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/cbs-should-have-to-release-transcripts-in-future-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据媒体监管机构集团称，哥伦比亚广播公司的新闻应该被要求在其广播计划中的未来政治访谈中主动释放所有成绩单60分钟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/cbs-should-have-to-release-transcripts-in-future-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 15:46:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言委内瑞拉石油买家的25％“次要”关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周一威胁要对委内瑞拉购买石油和天然气的任何国家对25％的关税，从而使他与拉丁美洲国家的移民争执，这一举动有可能冒着全球能源贸易的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易谈判在比赛中越来越大，以避免特朗普4月2日的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/countries-race-to-avoid-trump-tariffs-in-final-sprint-to-april-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国的交叉责任中，在唐纳德·特朗普总统“解放日”之前的最后一周，美国关税的国家急于向白宫要求提供让步和其他防御性回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/countries-race-to-avoid-trump-tariffs-in-final-sprint-to-april-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大的Poilievre承诺比Carney更深入所得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/canada-election-poilievre-promises-deeper-income-tax-cut-than-carney</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守派领导人皮埃尔·波利夫（Pierre Poilievre）承诺比自由派领导人马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）更深入的所得税，因为两位政客参加了一场激烈的选举竞赛，以吸引以生活成本挣扎的选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/canada-election-poilievre-promises-deeper-income-tax-cut-than-carney</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 13:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Menendez的妻子对贿赂的审判结束了他的职业生涯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/bob-menendez-s-wife-on-trial-over-bribes-that-ended-his-career</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在前参议员鲍勃·梅伦德斯（Bob Menendez）的贿赂审判中，陪审员看到了他与妻子分享的房屋中的金条和现金，听说了一位腐败的商人给她的梅赛德斯·奔驰（Mercedes Benz），并观看了这对夫妇与埃及情报代理人用餐的视频。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/bob-menendez-s-wife-on-trial-over-bribes-that-ended-his-career</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国，俄罗斯团队在乌克兰举行“富有成效”演讲之后见面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/russia-and-us-teams-meet-after-ukraine-holds-productive-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和乌克兰队举行会谈的第二天，美国和俄罗斯官员将在沙特阿拉伯开会，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统推动在战争中取得停火的进步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/russia-and-us-teams-meet-after-ukraine-holds-productive-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 07:33:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前犹他州众议员米娅·洛夫（Mia Love）是第一位当选美国众议院的黑人共和党妇女</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-24/former-utah-rep-mia-love-the-first-black-republican-woman-elected-to-the-us-house-has-died</link>
      <description><![CDATA[盐湖城（AP）＆Mdash;前美国众议员米娅·洛夫（Mia Love）犹他州是海地移民的女儿，后者成为第一位当选国会的黑人共和党妇女，他于周日去世。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-24/former-utah-rep-mia-love-the-first-black-republican-woman-elected-to-the-us-house-has-died</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 02:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
